Reference

All functions

gene1

Example Gene 1 This is a genetic distance matrix of SNPs for 19 isolates of Salmonella enterica to be used with the Newick phylogenetic tree (example tree 1) and the optional meta data file (example meta 1).

gene2

Example Gene 2 This is a genetic distance matrix of SNPs for 19 isolates of Eschericia coli to be used with the Newick phylogenetic tree (example tree 2) and the optional meta data file (example meta 2).

gene3

Example Gene 3 This is a genetic distance matrix of SNPs for 14 isolates of Salmonella enterica sub species enterica to be used with the Newick phylogenetic tree (example tree 3) and the optional meta data file (example meta 3).

meta1

Example Meta 1 This is a meta data file for tip correction and adding a heatmap for 19 isolates of Salmonella enterica to be used with the Newick phylogenetic tree (example tree 1) and the optional genetic distance file (example gene 1).

meta2

Example Meta 2 This is a meta data file for tip correction for 19 isolates of Eschericia coli to be used with the Newick phylogenetic tree (example tree 2) and the optional genetic distance file (example gene 2).

meta3

Example Meta 3 This is a meta data file for tip correction for 19 isolates of Salmonella enterica sub species enterica to be used with the Newick phylogenetic tree (example tree 3) and the optional genetic distance file (example gene 3).

tree1

Example Tree 1 This is a Newick phylogenetic tree for 19 isolates of Salmonella enterica to be used with the optional genetic distance matrix (example gene 1) and the optional meta data file (example meta 1).

tree2

Example Tree 2 #' This is a Newick phylogenetic tree for 19 isolates of Eschericia coli to be used with the optional genetic distance matrix (example gene 2) and the optional meta data file (example meta 2).

tree3

Example Tree 3 This is a Newick phylogenetic tree for 19 isolates of Salmonella enterica sub species enterica to be used with the genetic distance matrix (example gene 3) and the optional meta data file (example meta 3).
